  "detailed_description": "Explore dozens of Islands, both below and above the ocean water.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947200/extras/st6_c.PNG?t=1717814604\" /></span><br><br>Find secret locations and follow in the footsteps of another surviour of a ship that crashed on the Island.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947200/extras/st3_c.PNG?t=1717814604\" /></span><br><br>Experience flying as a bird to explore impossible to reach places in the sky.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947200/extras/st10_c.PNG?t=1717814604\" /></span><br><br>Travel the waters of the ocean as a human, or as a shark.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947200/extras/st9_c.PNG?t=1717814604\" /></span><br><br>17 Current skills in the game which offer unqiue and new experiences to change the pace of your adventure.<br>Including Woodcutting, Mining, Gathering, Fishing, Hunting, Farming, Thieving, Agility, Smithing, Crafting, Construction, Exploring, Archaeology, Cooking and three combat styles of Melee, Range and Magic.<br><br>Tutorial Quests which can be completed if the player so chooses, though completing them boosts your characters potential early on.<br><br>Singleplayer or Coop with friends. Hop into a game with your friend at any point of the main quest line and experience all the above together!",
  "about_the_game": "Explore dozens of Islands, both below and above the ocean water.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947200/extras/st6_c.PNG?t=1717814604\" /></span><br><br>Find secret locations and follow in the footsteps of another surviour of a ship that crashed on the Island.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947200/extras/st3_c.PNG?t=1717814604\" /></span><br><br>Experience flying as a bird to explore impossible to reach places in the sky.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947200/extras/st10_c.PNG?t=1717814604\" /></span><br><br>Travel the waters of the ocean as a human, or as a shark.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2947200/extras/st9_c.PNG?t=1717814604\" /></span><br><br>17 Current skills in the game which offer unqiue and new experiences to change the pace of your adventure.<br>Including Woodcutting, Mining, Gathering, Fishing, Hunting, Farming, Thieving, Agility, Smithing, Crafting, Construction, Exploring, Archaeology, Cooking and three combat styles of Melee, Range and Magic.<br><br>Tutorial Quests which can be completed if the player so chooses, though completing them boosts your characters potential early on.<br><br>Singleplayer or Coop with friends. Hop into a game with your friend at any point of the main quest line and experience all the above together!",
